## Hello World

```python
from vkbottle.bot import Bot

bot = Bot("GroupToken")

@bot.on.message()
async def handler(_) -> str:
    return "Hello, World!"

bot.run_forever()
```

[Смотреть больше примеров!](https://github.com/vkbottle/vkbottle/tree/master/examples)

